RE mmbtu Deal at CECTRKLFYI I rebooked the deal so that you are selling directly to Direct Energy and I let confirms know about it I talked to Canada and they would like for you to write an annuity to them for the difference in price that you were selling to them and the price that they were selling to Direct Energy I told them that I would talk to you on Monday and get back to them Thanks Stephanie Hopkins Enron Net Works Risk Management Original Message From Cuilla Martin Sent Friday October PM To Hopkins Stephanie Subject FW mmbtu Deal at CECTRKL Stephanie please make sure this gets rebooked and confirmed at a trade directly between ENA and Direct Energy Original Message From Webner Laura E Sent Friday October AM To Cuilla Martin Cc Oh Grant Boulanger Patricia Subject mmbtu Deal at CECTRKL Martin the deal I mentioned to you this morning is Presently we are buying from you and selling to Direct Energy Marketing Limited We need to step out of this deal and have you paper the trade between ENA and Direct If you require any information regarding this counterparty or contact information please contact Grant Oh in our office Thanks Laura
